      "source": [
        "# Final Project: Kalshi Market Making in short-dated SPX Events"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "bc3dd972",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Chris Mulligan (12502987), George Lord (12243747), Max Zhalilo (12341701)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "a4d7ac95",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# Content\n",
        "\n",
        "0. Abstract\n",
